text: Elimination Chamber (2014) (also known as No Escape (2014) in Germany) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on February 23, 2014 at the Target Center in Minneapolis, Minnesota. It was the fifth Elimination Chamber event held by WWE. There were two main events. The first saw The Wyatt Family defeat The Shield and the second saw Randy Orton successfully retain his WWE World Heavyweight Championship in an Elimination Chamber match against Daniel Bryan, John
